### Schema Provisioning

On first run, the workflow automatically provisions your agent schema. You can also do it manually:

```bash
curl -X POST ${DATA_INGESTION_BASE_URL}/admin/schema/provision/agent \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{"organisation_id":"YOUR_ORG_ID","agent_id":"YOUR_AGENT_ID"}'
```

