## Scheduled Jobs

This system uses OpenClaw cron for scheduling. The `setup.sh` script auto-registers these jobs:

${CRON_TABLE}

Manage jobs with:
```bash
openclaw cron list              # view all jobs
openclaw cron runs              # view run history
openclaw cron run --name <job>  # trigger manually
openclaw cron disable --name <job>  # pause a job
openclaw cron enable --name <job>   # resume a job
```

